Filtering Techniques:
[+] Server side or Client Side
[+] Extension Validation
[+] File Type Filtering
    [+] MIME (Multipurpose Internet Mail Extension) ==> Content-type in request Format: type/sub-type
    [+] Magic Number Validation ==> 89 50 4E 47 0D 0A 1A 0A ~ PNG format 
[+] File Length Filtering
[+] File name Filtering


Tricks to bypass Client Side Filtering
[+] Turning off JavaScript in the browser
[+] Intercepting and modifying the incomming page ==> preventing the page to use JavaScript
[+] Intercept and modify the upload 
[+] Send the file directly to the server ==> curl -X POST -F "submit:<value>" -F "<file-parameter>:@<path-to-file>" <site>
[+] PHP ==> https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PHP
[+] Magic Number Validation ==> File Extension https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_file_signatures


#directory indexing turned off ==> Access the file directly using the URL
